026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/umar-fears\/","url_meta":{"origin":24987,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Umar afraid they take Allah\u2019s mercy for granted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGo out and announce to the people that whoever testifies there is no God but Allah will surely enter Paradise.\u201d I went out and was met by Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said, \u201cReturn to the Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33832,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/10\/umar-silence-some-falsehood\/","url_meta":{"origin":24987,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Silence: Some falsehood is defeated by ignoring it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Yusuf reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnow that Allah has servants who cause some falsehood to die out by ignoring it and they give life to the truth by mentioning it.\u201d Source: Kita\u0304b al-Kharra\u0304j 1\/23 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u064a\u0648\u0633\u0641 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u06